WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.920
Are you manually copy-pasting text into ChatGPT to analyze your data?

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:05.080
Instead, try MOL!

00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:09.560
MOL is an R and Python package that brings the power of large language models directly

00:00:09.560 --> 00:00:11.080
into your data science flow.

00:00:11.080 --> 00:00:15.880
Instead of jumping between tabs, you can now run NLP operations like sentiment analysis,

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:19.240
summarization, and translation directly on your Data Frames.

00:00:19.240 --> 00:00:24.360
The package works row-wise, so you can process thousands of entries with just a single line

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:25.360
of code.

00:00:25.360 --> 00:00:30.400
You can run those locally, via Olama, or connect to legacy providers like OpenAI.

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:36.200
And if you use the tidy version R or Polars in Python, MOL fits your existing pipelines

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:38.799
with easy to see-to-use Python functions.

00:00:38.799 --> 00:00:39.400
Try MOL today!

